replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8d4b5d3fec91a1540dfc84ddc7508d3ffbb0fc","tid":337532,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:52:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n請問你櫃薪定日薪定月薪?</blockquote><br />\n日薪900<br />\n咩都拆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇黎咩貨<br />\n不過好甘 就轉行 條腰頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你返工有幾多個人一齊拆呀?<br />\n<br />\n我今日3個人拆40呎櫃集運貨...<br />\n<br />\n返到屋企條腰同頸開始痛...好佩服順豐每日專拆噸車果班...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都做過一排拆順豐噸車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你放工條腰真係唔撚使要"},{"pid":"b05865ad41db4b0f8c8c6ce7789dcf3da4177ac4","tid":337532,"uid":7146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"係fb比人伏左一次去做順豐拆櫃 做到食飯 食完飯隻手郁都郁唔到 伸都伸唔直 番到去肌肉痛左幾日 仲要得四舊水 我平時賭波買一場盤都唔撚止啦 從此唔再上fb搵工 都發誓唔會再做體力勞動工作"},{"pid":"53a9b934895aa0fc4f7ffdada597e6645372e66d","tid":337532,"uid":40422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:02:51.000Z","msg":"要體力勞動唔做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼學到樣技能先<br />\n老實講真係睇唔起做呢d既人  浪費人生"},{"pid":"c3f8da83006cd02e3c38eba3966b282eda33ccf6","tid":337532,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要體力勞動唔做地盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼學到樣技能先<br />\n老實講真係睇唔起做呢d既人  浪費人生</blockquote><br />\n其實拆櫃撈得掂自己接櫃做 唔差得過地盤姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有本事拆 拆得快唔易架 一樣可以搵好多"},{"pid":"2ba28c421e1f7e5e63b47f62418ffa9e761cff36","tid":337532,"uid":7146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係fb比人伏左一次去做順豐拆櫃 做到食飯 食完飯隻手郁都郁唔到 伸都伸唔直 番到去肌肉痛左幾日 仲要得四舊水 我平時賭波買一場盤都唔撚止啦 從此唔再上fb搵工 都發誓唔會再做體力勞動工作</blockquote><br />\n記得有個四眼肥仔都係炒散做順豐拆櫃 見到佢有上連登 好似叫唔知乜鋒 如果佢見到呢個post 我好想同佢講一句 我屌你老母啊死仆街 做多我幾日扮撚晒老seafood 慢慢做份垃圾牛工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6140514cc569cf746dbafb5ef2b401c87380b5a7","tid":337532,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>係fb比人伏左一次去做順豐拆櫃 做到食飯 食完飯隻手郁都郁唔到 伸都伸唔直 番到去肌肉痛左幾日 仲要得四舊水 我平時賭波買一場盤都唔撚止啦 從此唔再上fb搵工 都發誓唔會再做體力勞動工作</blockquote><br />\n記得有個四眼肥仔都係炒散做順豐拆櫃 見到佢有上連登 好似叫唔知乜鋒 如果佢見到呢個post 我好想同佢講一句 我屌你老母啊死仆街 做多我幾日扮撚晒老seafood 慢慢做份垃圾牛工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n天水圍？"},{"pid":"a3c9b61bc8141ca0f1f7663ee7ba35c8d3faa45c","tid":337532,"uid":65975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"拆過一日 9個鐘 得$600<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a5ebdcb99cf51620202991b76b2c4d909961c4","tid":337532,"uid":130495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:04:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgm